<section id="soluciones" class="bg-[#F5F7FA] py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto"><div class="mb-14"><p class="text-[#78BE20] text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] mb-2">Nuestros servicios</p><h2 class="text-[#0F2E65] text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">Soluciones</h2><div class="w-14 h-1 bg-[#78BE20] mt-4 rounded-full"></div></div><div class="relative space-y-6"><div class="group relative rounded-[2rem] bg-[#0F2E65] overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-500" style="z-index: 10;"><div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-[#78BE20] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div><div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-stretch"><div class="flex-1 p-8 md:p-10 lg:p-12"><span class="inline-block text-[#78BE20] text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] mb-3">CONECTIVIDAD</span><h3 class="text-white text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 tracking-tight">Conectividad</h3><p class="text-white/70 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 max-w-lg">Soluciones de enlace de alta disponibilidad y baja latencia. Optimizamos la comunicación de tu empresa con infraestructura de vanguardia que garantiza la continuidad de tu negocio en todo momento.</p><div class="w-full h-px bg-white/10 mb-6"></div><div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8"><div class="group/item flex flex-col items-start gap-2.5"><div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover/item:bg-[#78BE20]/10 group-hover/item:border-[#78BE20]/30 transition-all duration-300"><Globe class="lucide lucide-globe w-5 h-5 text-white/50 group-hover/item:text-[#78BE20] transition-colors duration-300" /></div><span class="text-white/80 text-xs font-medium leading-tight">Internet Dedicado</span></div><div class="group/item flex flex-col items-start gap-2.5"><div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover/item:bg-[#78BE20]/10 group-hover/item:border-[#78BE20]/30 transition-all duration-300"><Wifi class="lucide lucide-wifi w-5 h-5 text-white/50 group-hover/item:text-[#78BE20] transition-colors duration-300" /></div><span class="text-white/80 text-xs font-medium leading-tight">Internet PyME</span></div><div class="group/item flex flex-col items-start gap-2.5"><div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover/item:bg-[#78BE20]/10 group-hover/item:border-[#78BE20]/30 transition-all duration-300"><Satellite class="lucide lucide-satellite w-5 h-5 text-white/50 group-hover/item:text-[#78BE20] transition-colors duration-300" /></div><span class="text-white/80 text-xs font-medium leading-tight">Internet Satelital</span></div></div><button class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#78BE20] text-[#0F2E65] px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-bold hover:bg-[#6aad1a] hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-[#78BE20]/25 transition-all duration-300 group/btn">DESCUBRE MAS<ArrowRight class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 group-hover/btn:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300" /></button></div><div class="lg:w-[340px] xl:w-[400px] flex-shrink-0 relative flex items-center justify-center p-6 lg:p-8 bg-[#0a1f45]/50"><div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-48 h-48 bg-[#4169E1]/20 rounded-full blur-[60px] pointer-events-none"></div><img alt="Conectividad" class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-[260px] h-auto object-contain drop-shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" src="/assets/sol-conectividad.png"></div></div></div><div class="group relative rounded-[2rem] bg-[#0F2E65] overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-500" style="z-index: 11;"><div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-[#78BE20] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div><div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-stretch"><div class="flex-1 p-8 md:p-10 lg:p-12"><span class="inline-block text-[#78BE20] text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] mb-3">SERVICIOS ADMINISTRADOS</span><h3 class="text-white text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 tracking-tight">Servicios Administrados</h3><p class="text-white/70 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 max-w-lg">Delegue la operatividad técnica a expertos. Monitoreo proactivo, soporte especializado y gestión integral de su infraestructura tecnológica para que su equipo se enfoque en lo que realmente importa: crecer.</p><div class="w-full h-px bg-white/10 mb-6"></div><div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8"><div class="group/item flex flex-col items-start gap-2.5"><div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover/item:bg-[#78BE20]/10 group-hover/item:border-[#78BE20]/30 transition-all duration-300"><Headphones class="lucide lucide-headphones w-5 h-5 text-white/50 group-hover/item:text-[#78BE20] transition-colors duration-300" /></div><span class="text-white/80 text-xs font-medium leading-tight">Comunicaciones Unificadas</span></div><div class="group/item flex flex-col items-start gap-2.5"><div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover/item:bg-[#78BE20]/10 group-hover/item:border-[#78BE20]/30 transition-all duration-300"><Wifi class="lucide lucide-wifi w-5 h-5 text-white/50 group-hover/item:text-[#78BE20] transition-colors duration-300" /></div><span class="text-white/80 text-xs font-medium leading-tight">Red WiFi</span></div><div class="group/item flex flex-col items-start gap-2.5"><div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover/item:bg-[#78BE20]/10 group-hover/item:border-[#78BE20]/30 transition-all duration-300"><Shield class="lucide lucide-shield w-5 h-5 text-white/50 group-hover/item:text-[#78BE20] transition-colors duration-300" /></div><span class="text-white/80 text-xs font-medium leading-tight">Ciberseguridad</span></div></div><button class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#78BE20] text-[#0F2E65] px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-bold hover:bg-[#6aad1a] hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-[#78BE20]/25 transition-all duration-300 group/btn">DESCUBRE MAS<ArrowRight class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 group-hover/btn:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300" /></button></div><div class="lg:w-[340px] xl:w-[400px] flex-shrink-0 relative flex items-center justify-center p-6 lg:p-8 bg-[#0a1f45]/50"><div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-48 h-48 bg-[#4169E1]/20 rounded-full blur-[60px] pointer-events-none"></div><img alt="Servicios Administrados" class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-[260px] h-auto object-contain drop-shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" src="/assets/sol-servicios.png"></div></div></div><div class="group relative rounded-[2rem] bg-[#0F2E65] overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-500" style="z-index: 12;"><div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-[#78BE20] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div><div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-stretch"><div class="flex-1 p-8 md:p-10 lg:p-12"><span class="inline-block text-[#78BE20] text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] mb-3">CIBERSEGURIDAD</span><h3 class="text-white text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 tracking-tight">Ciberseguridad</h3><p class="text-white/70 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 max-w-lg">Protección multicapa contra amenazas avanzadas. Implementamos estrategias de defensa, detección y respuesta rápida para blindar sus activos digitales y asegurar la integridad de su información más valiosa.</p><div class="w-full h-px bg-white/10 mb-6"></div><div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8"><div class="group/item flex flex-col items-start gap-2.5"><div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl flex items-cent