ext-xs font-medium leading-tight">Smart Cities</span></div><div class="group/item flex flex-col items-start gap-2.5"><div class="w-11 h-11 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover/item:bg-[#78BE20]/10 group-hover/item:border-[#78BE20]/30 transition-all duration-300"><Radio class="lucide lucide-radio w-5 h-5 text-white/50 group-hover/item:text-[#78BE20] transition-colors duration-300" /></div><span class="text-white/80 text-xs font-medium leading-tight">Consultoría Técnica</span></div></div><button class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#78BE20] text-[#0F2E65] px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-bold hover:bg-[#6aad1a] hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-[#78BE20]/25 transition-all duration-300 group/btn">DESCUBRE MAS<ArrowRight class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 group-hover/btn:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300" /></button></div><div class="lg:w-[340px] xl:w-[400px] flex-shrink-0 relative flex items-center justify-center p-6 lg:p-8 bg-[#0a1f45]/50"><div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-48 h-48 bg-[#4169E1]/20 rounded-full blur-[60px] pointer-events-none"></div><img alt="Proyectos Especiales" class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-[260px] h-auto object-contain drop-shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" src="/assets/sol-proyectos.png"></div></div></div></div></div></section>
